<i>There's a starman
waiting in the sky</i>

1428
01:42:40.905 --> 01:42:42.157
<i>He'd like to
come and meet us</i>

1429
01:42:42.239 --> 01:42:43.957
<i>But he thinks
he'd blow our minds</i>

