1453
01:45:21.190 --> 01:45:23.864
<i>I've been thinking
about laws on Mars.</i>

1454
01:45:24.527 --> 01:45:25.744
<i>There's an
international treaty</i>

1455
01:45:25.861 --> 01:45:27.033
<i>saying no country
can lay claim...</i>

1456
01:45:27.196 --> 01:45:28.573
<i>to anything that's
not on Earth.</i>

1457
01:45:28.739 --> 01:45:29.831
<i>And by another treaty.</i>

1458
01:45:29.907 --> 01:45:31.875
<i>if you're not in any
